Package: a2a-gateway-sandbox
Version: 0.9.0
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.12), sqlite3, curl
Maintainer: A2A Team <team@greenhelix.net>
Section: web
Priority: optional
Description: A2A Commerce Gateway — sandbox deployment
 Sandbox instance of the A2A gateway running on port 8002
 with separate data directory at /var/lib/a2a-sandbox/.
 Databases are wiped on each deploy for a clean developer experience.
 Does not manage nginx or ufw (handled by production package).
